2026-01-13T16:17:31.0104030Z  * OPUS_CHECK_ASM, enable bit-exactness checks between optimized and c implementations.
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0104662Z  * OPUS_DNN_FLOAT_DEBUG, Run DNN computations as float for debugging purposes.
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0105389Z  * OPUS_DRED, enable DRED.
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0105647Z  * OPUS_OSCE, enable OSCE.
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0105980Z  * OPUS_FIXED_POINT_DEBUG, debug fixed-point implementation.
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0106483Z  * OPUS_USE_ALLOCA, use alloca for stack arrays (on non-C99 compilers).
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0107273Z  * OPUS_NONTHREADSAFE_PSEUDOSTACK, use a non threadsafe pseudostack when neither variable length arrays or alloca is supported.
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0108052Z  * OPUS_FAST_MATH, enable fast math (unsupported and discouraged use, as code is not well tested with this build option).
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0108697Z  * OPUS_X86_PRESUME_SSE4_1, assume target CPU has SSE4.1 support (override runtime check).
2026-01-13T16:17:31.0109237Z  * OPUS_X86_PRESUME_AVX2, assume target CPU has AVX FMA AVX2 support (override runtime check).
